## ğŸš€ Quickstart

### ğŸ“¦ Requirements

- Python 3.10+
- `rich` library

Install dependencies:

```bash
sudo apt install python3-rich
```
or

```bash
pip install rich
```

### â–¶ï¸ Run the app

```bash
python main.py
```

---

## âŒ¨ï¸ Commands

| Command     | Description                       |
|-------------|-----------------------------------|
| `:a`        | Add a new task                    |
| `:m`        | Move a task to another status     |
| `:d`        | Delete a task                     |
| `:e`        | Edit a task                       |
| `:f`        | Filter tasks by status/category   |
| `:s`        | Sort tasks by ID, title, category |
| `:search`   | Search for text in tasks          |
| `:c`        | Change a categoryâ€™s color         |
| `:layout`   | Switch layout (columns/rows)      |
| `:w`        | Save all changes                  |
| `:q`        | Quit                              |
| `:clear`    | Re-render the full board          |

