---

## ğŸ“ Configuration

All configuration (category colors, layout) is stored in `config.py` as a dictionary:

```python
CONFIG = {
    "category_colors": {
        "code": "cyan",
        "shop": "green",
    },
    "layout": "columns"
}
```

Colors are randomly assigned to new categories (avoiding duplicates), but can
be changed by the user with `:c`.

